                  <h3 class="point">How to copy an event</h3>
                  <p>Drag &amp; Drop event on calendar to move specify date.</p>
                  <p>Drag &amp; Drop with option-key to copy event.</p>


                  <h3 class="point">Hot to delete an event</h3>
                  <p>Click event you want to delete and press <em>Delete-key</em>.</p>


                  <h3 class="point">Keyboard operation</h3>
                  <!--<p>メニューに存在する項目以外にも、以下のキーを単独で押すとカレンダーの表示位置を移動できます。</p> -->
                  <div class="row">
                     <div class="span1 offset1">t</div><div class="span4">Go to today</div><div class="span2">&nbsp;</div>
                     <div class="span1 offset1">k</div><div class="span4">Go to previous week</div><div class="span2">&nbsp;</div>
                     <div class="span1 offset1">j</div><div class="span4">Go to next week</div><div class="span2">&nbsp;</div>
                     <div class="span1 offset1">p</div><div class="span4">Go to previous month</div><div class="span2">&nbsp;</div>
                     <div class="span1 offset1">n</div><div class="span4">Go to next month</div><div class="span2">&nbsp;</div>
                  </div>


                  <h3 class="point">How to create new calendar, edit calendar color</h3>
                  <p>You can edit existing calendar on <a href="ical://">Calendar.app</a>.
                  Open Calendar.app and choose ”New Calendar” in File menu to create new calendar.</p>
                  <p>If you want to edit calendar color, right-click on calendar name and choose Get Info.</p>
                  <p><img class="quick img-rounded" src="./calendar-add-en.png" /></p>

