               <div class="span8">

                  <h3 class="point">Calendar date or week is wrong</h3>
                  <p>Please check TimeZone setting if date or week is wrong.</p>
                  <ul>
                     <li>Moca &gt; Preferences &gt; Time Zone</li>
                     <li>System Preferences &gt; Date &amp; Time &gt; Time Zone</li>
                  </ul>


                  <h3 class="point">Event has unregistered alert</h3>
                  <p>Please check calendar.app preference.</p>
                  <ul>
                     <li><a href="ical://">Calendar.app</a> &gt; Preferences &gt; Alerts</li>
                  </ul>

